info.name: litestash
info.summary: The LiteStash Python project offers a lightning-fast, lightweight key-value storage solution.  LiteStash provides a NoSQL API for seamless integration into your applications.  The LiteStash database handles the data with SQLite transparently.  Optimal use for caching, session management, and other high-performance use cases.
